                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Personally I think bidding systems are unfair.
<br />

<br />
Example:  
<br />
First raid of time, Etheral Silk Leggs drop at the time there are only 10 casters in guild
<br />

<br />
Two months later same item drops, but inbetween this time the guild increased its count t 15, same item, now the 2nd person has to pay more simply because the guild recruited more of said class type that did nothing but pad the auction.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
